  • Jaguar (⭐464) - A server framework built for speed, simplicity and extensibility.

    • There are many packages written for Shelf. By convention they start with shelf_.

  • Rikulo Stream (⭐235) - Lightweight web server with request routing, filtering, template engine, WebSocket, MVC design pattern, and file-based static resources.
